name: [Guest user][.com]Place order using all shipping methods - STM, BOPIS, SDD

steps.name: Given Guest User should be on michaels home page
When user adds products with "Store Pickup ,Ship to Me ,Same Day Delivery" shipping method to the cart
And User should click on checkout button
And User will get model popup to click on continue as guest user
When User should provides shipping information like Valid First Name, Last Name,Addressline1 Addressline2,city,state,zipcode,email and Phone number
And User will add the Card Details like Name on Card,Card Number,Expiration Date,CVV
And User will click on Place order button
Then User will redirected to Order Confirmation Page
And User should find Order confirmation with order number
